Hello there, we have a awesome new version of Speaky available for you today.
We’ve squashed some pretty pesky bugs to improve your overall experience using the app — and we’ve enhanced our chat to help you learn and practice languages in the best environment!
Try it now!

Any Questions or Feedback? We’d love to hear from you! Leave us a review or send us your feedback at contact@gospeaky.com.
